L001:to:c:orientation-survival-001
MCP Shell swallows git stdout
Use udc:execute_command not Windows-MCP:Shell for git.

L002:to:c:orientation-survival-001
MCP Shell PATH resets every command
Each invocation fresh. Use full paths or udc:execute_command.

L003:to:c:orientation-survival-001+opus46-coldstart-recon-001
MCP Shell is PowerShell only AND fully broken on BIGSPIDER
FileNotFoundError on ALL commands. Use udc:execute_command + "C:\Program Files\PowerShell\7\pwsh.exe" for PS needs.

